#: front-page.php:33
msgid "Civic Engagement Tools"
msgstr "Mwan Civic Engagement"

#: front-page.php:33
msgid "for the People of Hawaii"
msgstr "ren aramas ren Hawaii"

#: front-page.php:43
msgid "Government information shouldn't require a law degree to navigate. Civi.Me makes it simple to stay informed, show up, and have your voice heard — in plain language, for free."
msgstr "Meinisin government esapw pwan fen mwo ekkena law degree ren aninis. Civi.Me nekukunis iten ikkena fen nuku, wor, a ura om angang — won language masowan, ese chommong."

#: front-page.php:53
msgid "What matters to you?"
msgstr "Nge ika ese chommong iei?"

#: front-page.php:56
msgid "Browse meetings"
msgstr "Katon meetings"

#: front-page.php:167
msgid "The challenge"
msgstr "Ewe sapwuk"

#: front-page.php:169
msgid "Civic participation should be accessible for all residents"
msgstr "Civic participation epwe wor ren aramas fonu ren ewe fengen"

#: front-page.php:172
msgid "People want to be engaged, but the barriers make it feel impossible. We're removing them."
msgstr "Aramas mochen katon engag, an ka wor barriers me nekukunis ika ese ekkewe. Sia tufichin ekkewe."

#: front-page.php:190
msgid "Buried information"
msgstr "Meinisin me siksiken"

#: front-page.php:191
msgid "Meeting agendas are buried in PDFs across dozens of county and state websites with no consistent format."
msgstr "Meeting agendas siksiken won PDFs won fonu ren county a state websites ese wor format me kakaten."

#: front-page.php:203
msgid "No timely alerts"
msgstr "Esap wor alerts fen manaw"

#: front-page.php:204
msgid "Residents find out about decisions that affect their neighborhoods after the fact — if at all."
msgstr "Aramas nuku iei fen nuku ren decisions me affetin neighborhood masowan mwuri — ika ese wor."

#: front-page.php:219
msgid "Bureaucratic language"
msgstr "Language ren government"

#: front-page.php:220
msgid "Government documents are written for lawyers, not residents. Plain-language summaries are rare."
msgstr "Government documents nekukun ren lawyers, esap ren aramas nuku. Summaries won plain language momokutu."

#: front-page.php:234
msgid "Who are my representatives?"
msgstr "Ifa representatives omw?"

#: front-page.php:235
msgid "Most residents can't name their city council member, let alone their neighborhood board chair."
msgstr "Aramas nuku fonu ese katon iniseiso city council member masowan, ese puan board chair ren neighborhood masowan."

#: front-page.php:254
msgid "Start here"
msgstr "Angang iteni iei"

#: front-page.php:256
msgid "Tell us what matters to you"
msgstr "Ura ren sigih nge ika ese chommong iei"

#: front-page.php:259
msgid "Pick the topics you care about — environment, housing, education, health — and we'll show you the government meetings and councils that handle those issues."
msgstr "Tori topics me ke mwich ren — environment, housing, education, health — a sia katon meetings a councils ren government me anganganis ekkewe."

