#: front-page.php:305
msgid "Pick the topics you care about and we'll show you the meetings that matter."
msgstr "Tori topics me ke mwich ren a sia katon meetings me chommong."

#: front-page.php:320
msgid "Civic tools"
msgstr "Mwan civic"

#: front-page.php:322
msgid "What you can do on Civi.Me"
msgstr "Nge ika ke angang won Civi.Me"

#: front-page.php:363
#: front-page.php:403
#: front-page.php:443
#: front-page.php:487
msgid "Live"
msgstr "Nuku"

#: front-page.php:365
msgid "Browse Meetings"
msgstr "Katon Meetings"

#: front-page.php:368
msgid "All public meetings — boards, commissions, and councils — in one calendar. Filter by topic, council, or date. AI-generated summaries explain what's on the agenda."
msgstr "Meetings fonu ren aramas — boards, commissions, a councils — won emon calendar. Filter won topic, council, a fono. AI summaries kopwe ura nge ika won agenda."

#: front-page.php:405
msgid "Council Profiles"
msgstr "Profiles ren Councils"

#: front-page.php:408
msgid "Learn what each board and commission actually does — in plain language. See who sits on the board, upcoming meetings, open seats, and how to participate."
msgstr "Nuku nge ika board a commission anganganis — won plain language. Katon ifa puan iei won board, meetings me fis, open seats, a ita fen participate."

#: front-page.php:445
msgid "Get Alerts"
msgstr "Anisi Alerts"

#: front-page.php:448
msgid "Subscribe to topics or specific councils. Get email alerts when meetings are scheduled — before it's too late to participate."
msgstr "Subscribe won topics a councils. Anisi email alerts me meetings schedule — mwo ita ese wor manaw ren participate."

#: front-page.php:489
msgid "Guides & Compliance"
msgstr "Guides a Compliance"

#: front-page.php:492
msgid "Step-by-step civic action guides plus compliance tools for agencies — Sunshine Law, public records, accessibility, and public participation best practices."
msgstr "Guides civic action step-by-step a mwan compliance ren agencies — Sunshine Law, public records, accessibility, a best practices ren public participation."

#: front-page.php:511
msgid "What we believe"
msgstr "Nge ika sia mochen"

#: front-page.php:513
msgid "Information access is a community right"
msgstr "Access ren meinisin ewe right ren community"

#: front-page.php:516
msgid "Every resident deserves to know what decisions are being made that affect their community — in language they can understand, at a time when they can still participate."
msgstr "Aramas fonu ren emon fonufan epwe nuku ren decisions me affet masowan community — won language me konong, won manaw me chok fen participate."

#: front-page.php:534
msgid "Strictly nonpartisan"
msgstr "Ese chok ren emon party"

#: front-page.php:535
msgid "Civi.Me does not endorse candidates, parties, or positions on any issue. We present facts: what a bill does, who submitted it, when the hearing is. We provide tools and templates — never talking points."
msgstr "Civi.Me ese support candidates, parties, a positions won nge ika issue. Sia katon facts: nge ika bill anganganis, ifa me submit, manaw ren hearing. Sia hawi mwan a templates — esap puan talking points."

#: front-page.php:549
msgid "Everyone is included — no exceptions"
msgstr "Aramas fonu wor — esap wor exception"

#: front-page.php:550
msgid "We use \"residents\" — not \"citizens.\" We support all 15 languages recognized by Hawaii's Office of Language Access. We build for mobile and include a phone line for people who don't have a smartphone at all."
msgstr "Sia angang \"aramas nuku\" — esap \"citizens.\" Sia support languages 15 me Hawaii's Office of Language Access fen nunun. Sia kukun ren mobile a include line telefon ren aramas ese wor smartphone."

#: front-page.php:561
msgid "Cultural respect is not optional"
msgstr "Respect ren culture esap optional"

#: front-page.php:562
msgid "Native Hawaiian sovereignty is a living issue, not history. We frame civic participation as community engagement — not blind deference to government structures."
msgstr "Sovereignty ren Native Hawaiian ewe issue me nuku, esap history. Sia katon civic participation ika community engagement — esap chok kopwe tongeni government."

#: front-page.php:573
msgid "Open source and community-built"
msgstr "Open source a kukun community"

#: front-page.php:574
msgid "Civi.Me's code is public on GitHub from day one. Civic infrastructure should be open to inspection, contribution, and community ownership. If we ever make a decision you disagree with, you can see exactly why — and you can help us do better."
msgstr "Code ren Civi.Me public won GitHub mei iten fono senisin. Civic infrastructure epwe wor ren inspection, contribution, a ownership ren community. Ika sia angang emon decision me ke ese tongeni, ke katon nge ura — a ke puan tongeni koukuei sia angang mwirin."

#: front-page.php:589
msgid "Join us"
msgstr "Fen wor sigih"

#: front-page.php:591
msgid "Help build civic infrastructure for Hawaii"
msgstr "Koukuei kukun civic infrastructure ren Hawaii"

#: front-page.php:594
msgid "Civi.Me is open source and community-driven. Whether you're a developer, a civic advocate, or just someone who cares — there's a place for you."
msgstr "Civi.Me open source a community-driven. Ika developer, civic advocate, a ika chok aramas me mwich — wor fonu ren omw."

